<plot>Five friends in an old bus across Europe. Both John Arild and Nikolai have spinal muscle atrophy. Their muscles go weaker and weaker. This is their chance to fulfill a dream of traveling across Europe together and experience the different countries just as anybody else can do. It's a warm and touching story about friendship, thoughtfulness and courage.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?183515</url></doc>
